title: Jefferson Airplane - complete discography
description:
The complete Jefferson Airplane albums discography including :
- Takes off (1966)
- Surrealistic pillow (1967)
- After bathing at Baxters (1968)
- Crown of creation (1968)
- Bless its pointed little head (1969)
- Volunteers (1970)
- The worst of J.A. (compilation - 1970)
- Bark (1971)
- Long John Silver (1972)

Nota : The Jefferson Starship discography is not included.
